overhead, you know how it is.

545
00:39:55,935 --> 00:39:58,145
No, I expect that
you wouldn't know.

546
00:40:01,983 --> 00:40:04,401
Leave your address
with my office.

547
00:40:04,486 --> 00:40:09,364
I'll pick you up Friday
at 8:00 and we'll eat.

548
00:40:17,499 --> 00:40:20,084
One more thing.
Do you have a name,

549
00:40:20,168 --> 00:40:22,211
