God, that's wonderful.

652
00:51:00,725 --> 00:51:03,560
Well, there's no accounting
for taste, is there?

653
00:51:06,647 --> 00:51:07,939
Should I marry her?

654
00:51:08,065 --> 00:51:09,399
God. Right.

655
00:51:11,402 --> 00:51:12,819
