750
01:00:35,007 --> 01:00:36,382
You won't.

751
01:00:36,758 --> 01:00:37,925
Why would I not?

752
01:00:38,010 --> 01:00:41,012
Because I keep the Russians
from knowing you work for us.

753
01:00:41,888 --> 01:00:43,889
You quit working for me,

754
